image_analysis.description: A photograph of an open closet or storage unit containing various items. On the top shelf are two white female torso mannequins. The shelves below contain athletic equipment including sneakers, a blue exercise mat, a black storage bin with labels, stacks of small boxes (possibly DVDs or supplements), push-up bars, and other fitness accessories. To the left, a large stone-like sculpture or bust is partially visible on a counter next to a set of white drawers. A black pole (possibly a weight bar or cleaning tool) leans against the shelves.
image_analysis.layout: The image shows a built-in shelving unit flanked by white cabinetry and a doorway/wall. The photograph is taken from a straight-on perspective.
